20:18.302 --> 20:20.512
- We were at the library. Again.

20:20.512 --> 20:24.099
- I have to write a 50-page paper
on the effects of beach erosion.

20:24.099 --> 20:27.019
Can I please just borrow
the Useless Homework ray once?

20:27.019 --> 20:28.395
- No. No rays in this house!

20:28.395 --> 20:29.438
