20:30.022 --> 20:32.691
- Yaya.
Oh, hello Mr. Sarner.

20:32.691 --> 20:34.026
You wanna come over tonight?

20:34.026 --> 20:36.612
Oh, tonight is not good actually,
Korvo has the shits--

20:36.612 --> 20:37.654
Okay.

20:37.654 --> 20:39.656
Ugh. That was Mr. Sarner.

20:39.656 --> 20:41.491
He invited himself and his wife
over for dinner,

20:41.491 --> 20:42.743
and they want veal parmesan.

20:42.743 --> 20:46.163
- But I'm making ginger-glazed salmon
with a cucumber dill salad.

20:46.163 --> 20:48.165
- Well, now you're making
veal fuckin' parmesan!

20:48.165 --> 20:50.959
And you have half an hour do to it,
or we'll get fired from our work job!

20:50.959 --> 20:52.002
[sighs]

20:52.002 --> 20:54.004
- Are these really
the stakes of our lives now?

20:54.004 --> 20:57.257
Remember when we saved humanity
from ice lava and napadoodles

20:57.257 --> 20:59.510
and fought over who had
more Christmas spirit?

20:59.510 --> 21:02.804
- I spent 14 minutes in heaven
with a janky BTS!

21:02.804 --> 21:06.183
- Korvo turned into goo, and I had
to fight my ex-lover Malcolm Gladwell!

21:06.183 --> 21:07.559
- Oh, those were the days.

21:07.559 --> 21:09.978
We used to do so much crazy
sci-fi stuff.

21:11.021 --> 21:12.356
- I love you guys.

21:12.773 --> 21:14.525
And I love Moana.

21:15.317 --> 21:17.277
- It's worth it. For the Pupa.

21:17.861 --> 21:19.238
JESSE/TERRY/YUMYULACK:
For the Pupa.

21:19.238 --> 21:20.447
- Ahhh! Fuck!

21:20.447 --> 21:21.823
- Yeah, buddy.

21:21.823 --> 21:24.117
- Goddammit, is Little Buddy
just gonna be, like,

21:24.117 --> 21:26.328
fuckin' around all the time now
or something?

21:26.328 --> 21:28.121
- Yep. This is our life now.

